This code is licensed under the terms of the Lesser GNU Public Licence
(LGPL).  See the file COPYING for details.

Documentation will follow in the near future.  Current focus is on
stabilizing the project's Scheme and PF interpreters,  which are
intended to be embedded in an application as a static library.

No ./configure script yet

Building
--------

Type "make" at the top level directory.
This produces sc/sc and pf/pf.

Both applications need to run in their own directory to find their boot scripts.


Dependencies
------------

The usual (GNU make + GCC) plus

`mzscheme' for bootstrap code generation
http://plt-scheme.org

`leg' for the s-expression parser 
http://piumarta.com/software/peg/

`ffmpeg' for the media library.  Use a recent SVN snapshot.  Revision
20455 works (2009/11/5).
